==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*ἀγρός / agros / ag-ros'

===Etymology===
*From [[ἄγω]] {{GG|71}}; a [[field]] (as a drive for cattle); generally the country; specifically a farm, that is, [[hamlet]]: 

===Noun===
'''ἀγρός'''

# [[country]], [[farm]], piece of [[ground]], [[land]].

